{
  "stem": "15686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was our recreation, because the neighbors complained that there was too much noise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when school was out, the teachers would come out on the street and make sure that we were very quiet, and there was nobody shouting or yelling or anything else.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They weren't there to help us much with the Hitler Youth gangs, but they made sure that the neighbors weren't disturbed, because the penalty was that the government would close down the school.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we were very cowed and very subdued in school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had to really toe the line.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And those were the first impacts that I felt as a child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, back home, eventually we picked up bits of conversation where my father said, well, you know so-and-so has been my customer for 25 years.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And now he says he won't buy for me anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He's afraid he's going to get into trouble.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I lost his good account.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it became more and more difficult for my father to earn a living, because his Gentile customers were afraid, although they were his friends, and they knew him for all these years.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my father had a very, very difficult time dealing with this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "As I said before, my father was German first and Jewish second.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He had been a volunteer in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was for four years on the French front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was decorated with the Iron Cross by the Kaiser himself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this was the proudest moment of his life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he walked around every day of his life with that Iron Cross in his pocket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I remember once as a big joke, which got my brother and myself into a lot of trouble, we took the Iron Cross.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
